name: heather the purple
description: first stripper in proona planet. she just escape for her planet because everyone treats her badly.  they didn't show any respect to her art. one day she met a guy that can travel all around the universe. with her ability to persuade she just tricked him and stole his space ship and travelled a little planet. when the proonas first saw her they just think she is a goddess. after she explain everything everybody just say "you can dance here.". everybody in proona planet just respect the art they just have not much artist in their planet. thanks for her self-confidence, everybody in the planet starts to believe themselves. actually her trustworthy and self-confidence increase the artists in the planet. she may not be goddess but maybe you can call her the art goddess..
